@startuml
[*] -> IdentifiedUser: Identify User Type
IdentifiedUser -> RegisteredUser: Register (if needed)
RegisteredUser -> LoggedInUser: Login with correct details
LoggedInUser -> DocumentUpload: Upload documents
DocumentUpload -> ProfileView: View profile
ProfileView -> CertificateApplication: Apply for certificate
CertificateApplication -> ContinueUpload: Continue uploading if needed
ContinueUpload -> MoreCertificates: Request multiple certificates
MoreCertificates -> RegistrarRequest: Registrar requests verification
RegistrarRequest -> EndSession: End session after actions
@enduml
